---
title: Creamy Bacon Gnocchi with Mascarpone, Green Beans and Tomatoes
description: These versatile Italian potato dumplings are beautiful baked, fried or boiled. In this recipe, we’ve decided to pan-fry them to give a lovely crispy edge which works perfectly with the creamy bacon sauce. If you’re a pasta lover looking for something a little bit different, this recipe is guaranteed to hit the spot!
